453 ♦? Suffering p? All. ...suffering can be avoided byrealizing that God
is the only reality.You are the manifestation of God, aspiritual being
emanating from the oneand only source, which is God. Yourspirit is
eternal—you live, breathe andhave your being in God. You cannotbe separated
from God, for God isthe totality and the only reality—God “is,” nothing
else is.
